.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad5f93c8edcac74aff8d9e565fbbce0e96b3a63","tid":781702,"uid":49094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"唔虐啦, 依家仲好down 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab65189424ed6c02050c94a9b8181b7c1faa522a","tid":781702,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T11:31:39.000Z","msg":"女主角真係好吸引"},{"pid":"555c90db3746853a591dafb0651af81e35109487","tid":781702,"uid":49094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"狩生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8892d68076ee54a8843f8acae4ffcdd0fece8944","tid":781702,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"如果係返去自己嘅中學時代就話姐<br />\n返去而家嘅中學時代<br />\n玩抖音咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1a3d60b2bc810c103fd3f5894ce87b9a1a804e","tid":781702,"uid":49094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8892d68076ee54a8843f8acae4ffcdd0fece8944","tid":781702,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"如果係返去自己嘅中學時代就話姐<br />\n返去而家嘅中學時代<br />\n玩抖音咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"又唔係想做, 只係話睇完套野好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15203b702ba8534ef49e6dbb8c5612b4f9639b8a","tid":781702,"uid":